 (who published my THE EYE, THE WALTZ INVENTION, THE QUARTET and my Russian translation of LOLITA) are on the brink of bankruptcy and are trying to dispose of their business. Oscar de Liso, who owns Phaedra, ran an ad to that effect.

Warm greetings from us both.





Yours ever,

Vladimir Nabokov





